      <title>英国警告欧盟新边境系统启用将导致边境延误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/uk-warns-of-border-delays-when-new-eu-border-system-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府警告称，欧盟将于十月份推出一项新系统，要求英国公民共享生物特征数据，届时英国游客应做好在边境高峰时段排长队准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/uk-warns-of-border-delays-when-new-eu-border-system-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
